📌 Concept Explanation

An EC2 instance is a virtual machine in AWS that allows you to run applications in the cloud.

It consists of:

Operating system (AMI)
CPU and memory configuration (instance type)
Network configuration (VPC + Security Group)
Authentication (Key Pair)
