ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa ec2-user@<public-ip>
🔐 Security Best Practices
Never expose SSH (port 22) to all IPs in production.
Use restricted IP ranges or VPN access.
Avoid hardcoding AMI IDs across regions.
Use least privilege security groups.
Tag resources properly for tracking and cost management.
Do not reuse the same key pair across environments.
