API backends
CI/CD runners
Microservices nodes

Experienced DevOps engineers think beyond “launching a server” and instead ask:

"How does this server fit into a scalable, secure, and automated architecture?"

From this point forward, everything you build should be viewed as part of a larger system design, not isolated resources.
